# gitops_secondTry

A minimal GitOps project using ArgoCD and Kubernetes.

## Structure

app/
- Flask web application
- Dockerfile to build container image

manifests/
- Kubernetes manifests
- Watched and reconciled by ArgoCD

## GitOps Flow

1. Build and push Docker image
2. Update image tag in manifests
3. Commit to Git
4. ArgoCD syncs cluster state automatically

## ArgoCD Configuration

- Repo Path: manifests/
- Namespace: default
- Sync: Manual or Auto
